name: (figured) of The Common Wishes to Conceive 01
description:
Heavily influenced by Bojack Horseman Quotes

"usually when poeple ask how I'm doing the real answer is I'm doing shitty

But I can't say I'm doing shitty

Because I don't have a good reason to be doing shitty."

to always had negative thoughts about myself, feeling shitty all the time.
As if nothing matters, as if I don't have a good life.

of The Common Wishes to Conceive is a series of mocking myself before anyone else did kust because I can, nothing more.

printed tracing paper on my 2020 sketchbook.

This work was meant to be my gratitude token to myself.
Editions and prices are numbered based on my personal interest.
Celebrating it with the people who have all my works (thank you indiedo and moriza, airdropped it to both of you :-) )
